 contributor who jumped in to help Gatsby docs keep becoming more polished, comprehensive, and clear. In fact, many of the PR’s fixed problems we hadn’t even created issues for yet! And we’re increasing the number of "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"hacktoberfest"}]},{"type":"text","value":" + "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"documentation"}]},{"type":"text","value":" labeled issues to account for the surge of helpful contributions. A special thanks to "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://github.com/amberleyromo"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"@amberleyromo"}]},{"type":"text","value":", "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://github.com/jlengstorf"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"@jlengstorf"}]},{"type":"text","value":", "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://github.com/DSchau"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"@DSchau"}]},{"type":"text","value":", and "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://github.com/pieh"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"@pieh"}]},{"type":"text","value":" for their hard work giving feedback and merging PR’s!"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Read more on how to participate in Gatsby Hacktoberfest in our "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"/blog/2018-10-09-hacktoberfest-kickoff/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hacktoberfest kickoff post"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"with-great-contributions-comes-great-responsibility"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#with-great-contributions-comes-great-responsibility","ariaLabel":"with great contributions comes great responsi